              "id": "CVE-2024-22243",
              "name": "LanguageSpecificPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "springframework: URL Parsing with Host Validation"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Applications that use UriComponentsBuilder to parse an externally provided URL (e.g. through a query parameter) AND perform validation checks on the host of the parsed URL may be vulnerable to a  open redirect https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/601.html  attack or to a SSRF attack if the URL is used after passing validation checks."
